labels.modelTypeCdHelp:
Fund Model type:
Flexible - Under this type, the allocation % for each Fund can be chosen by the Insured within pre-defined limits.
Fixed - Under this type, the allocation % for each Fund is fixed and not given as a choice to the Insured. On the UI, it is defaulted and read-only.
Fixed with override - In this case, although the allocation % for each Fund is defined at the Model level, it can be overridden by the Insured within pre-defined limits. On the UI it is defaulted and editable.
